articles.title: Club Officers
articles.summary: This document lists the club's officers and board members, and addresses the club's low treasury due to the lease of its observing site, requesting donations. It also reports on recent activities, including a January meeting featuring a talk on Pioneer 10/11 findings by NASA's Mr. Worthmann, and a January 11 star party at Mt. Umanhum, which, despite cold and windy conditions, was well-attended and enthusiastic.

articles.title: COMING EVENTS:
articles.summary: This article outlines upcoming events for an astronomy club from February to May 1975, including general meetings featuring talks on constellations and the Messier Catalog, star parties, and board meetings. It also includes a brief news note about members attending a W.A.A. meeting and an update on Dr. Gregory's health.
